<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>

<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>Capella Bakery & Cafe</title>

<link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

</head>

<body>

<header>

<div class="container">

<h1>Capella Bakery</h1>

<nav>
<a href="#about">About</a>
<a href="#menu">Menu</a>
<a href="#contact">Contact</a>
</nav>

</div>

</header>

<section class="hero">

<div class="hero-text">

<h2>Delicious Desserts & Cozy Cafe Vibes</h2>

<p>Fresh pastries, artisan coffee, and unforgettable flavors.</p>

<a href="#menu" class="btn">View Menu</a>

</div>

</section>

<section id="about" class="section">

<h2>About Us</h2>

<p>
At Capella Bakery we craft fresh pastries, breads and desserts daily.
Our cafe blends premium ingredients with cozy ambience to create a perfect
place for coffee, conversations and sweet moments.
</p>

</section>

<section id="menu" class="section menu">

<h2>Popular Items</h2>

<div class="menu-grid">

<div class="item">
<h3>Chocolate Cake</h3>
<p>₹250</p>
</div>

<div class="item">
<h3>Blueberry Cheesecake</h3>
<p>₹320</p>
</div>

<div class="item">
<h3>Cappuccino</h3>
<p>₹180</p>
</div>

<div class="item">
<h3>Butter Croissant</h3>
<p>₹150</p>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<section id="contact" class="section">

<h2>Visit Us</h2>

<p>Mangalore, Karnataka</p>

<div class="map">

<iframe
src="https://maps.google.com/maps?q=mangalore&t=&z=13&ie=UTF8&iwloc=&output=embed">
</iframe>

</div>

</section>

<footer>

<p>© 2026 Capella Bakery. All rights reserved.</p>

</footer>

<script src="script.js"></script>

</body>
</html>